@startuml sequence_diagram_prediksi
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Sequence Diagram Prediksi Risiko DBD\nSistem Prediksi Penyebaran DBD

actor "Pengguna" as User
participant "Halaman\nPrediksi" as Page
participant "Controller\nPrediksi" as Controller
participant "Python API\n(Flask)" as API
participant "Random Forest\nModel" as Model
database "Database" as DB

User -> Page : Buka menu Prediksi
activate Page

Page --> User : Tampilkan form input prediksi

User -> Page : Input parameter:\n- Bulan\n- Jumlah Kasus\n- Rata-rata Usia\n- Jenis Kelamin\n- Lama Rawat

User -> Page : Klik tombol Prediksi
Page -> Page : Validasi input

Page -> Controller : Submit data prediksi
activate Controller

Controller -> API : POST /predict\n{bulan, jumlah_kasus, usia, jk, lama_rawat}
activate API

API -> API : Load model dari file\n(random_forest_model.pkl)
API -> API : Load encoder

API -> Model : model.predict(features)
activate Model
Model --> API : prediction
deactivate Model

API -> Model : model.predict_proba(features)
activate Model
Model --> API : probabilities
deactivate Model

API -> API : Decode prediction\n(Tinggi/Sedang/Rendah)
API -> API : Generate rekomendasi

API -> DB : INSERT INTO hasil_prediksi\n(hasil, confidence)
activate DB
DB --> API : Success
deactivate DB

API --> Controller : Response\n{tingkat_risiko, confidence, probabilities, rekomendasi}
deactivate API

Controller --> Page : Kirim hasil prediksi

Page --> User : Tampilkan hasil:\n- Tingkat Risiko (dengan warna)\n- Confidence Score\n- Probabilitas per kategori\n- Rekomendasi tindakan

deactivate Controller
deactivate Page

@enduml
